title: Episode 150: 50 Shades of Mario (Feat. Mario)
itunes:title: Episode 150: 50 Shades of Mario (Feat. Mario)
description:
Singer Mario joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and he was not ready for what he had coming! Mario shares his regrets with how he's treated women in the past, limitations in the bedroom, posting thirst traps and much more. Enjoy!
